OL,3,CSwansea firefighter scales summit
OL,4,Ccarrying rowing machine for Atlantic
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FIn an extraordinary display of
OL,8,Fdedication, Swansea firefighter Mark
OL,9,FEdwards is taking his Atlantic Ocean
OL,10,Frowing challenge preparation to new
OL,11,Fheights ` literally.
OL,13,FThe 36-year-old has been rigorously
OL,14,Ftraining by carrying a 30kg rowing
OL,15,Fmachine to the 700ft summit of Kilvey
OL,16,FHill, Swansea's highest point.
