OL,7,FEdwards, from Mid and West Wales Fire
OL,8,Fand Rescue Service, is part of a four-
OL,9,Fperson crew (one male, two female)
OL,10,Fthat is aiming to row 3,000 miles
OL,11,Facross the Atlantic to raise money for
OL,12,Fthe Fire Fighters Charity.
OL,14,F"Being local, I've been trying to
OL,15,Fidentify unique spots that I can take
OL,16,Fmy rower to train," Mark told ITV
OL,17,FWales News.
OL,19,F"The opportunity that's been presented
OL,20,Fto me is a once-in-a-lifetime
OL,21,Fopportunity. It's incredible."
