OL,7,FFor several weeks, Edwards has been
OL,8,Flugging the 66lbs of equipment `
OL,9,Fcomparable in weight to a domestic
OL,10,Fwashing machine ` 213 meters to the
OL,11,Ftop of the sub marilyn.
OL,13,FThe crew is set to depart from La
OL,14,FGomera in the Canary Islands in
OL,15,FDecember 2026. The extreme challenge
OL,16,Fis anticipated to last up to six
OL,17,Fweeks, with the team rowing in two-
OL,18,Fhour shifts, two hours on and two
OL,19,Fhours off. They are fully self-
OL,20,Fsupported and hope to reach Antigua in
OL,21,Fearly 2027.
