OL,7,FThe next phase of Mark's training will
OL,8,Finvolve him and his teammates taking
OL,9,Ftheir ocean boat into the waters
OL,10,Faround Swansea Bay.
OL,12,FMark emphasises that his efforts are
OL,13,Ffor a vital cause.
