OL,7,F"The Fire Fighters Charity is a UK
OL,8,Forganisation which provides support
OL,9,Fand rehabilitation to serving and
OL,10,Fretired firefighters, which extends to
OL,11,Ffamily members as well," he explained.
OL,12,F"With the type of incidents that we
OL,13,Fmay come across and have to deal with,
OL,14,Fwe all need a little bit of downtime.
OL,15,FSo that's what they assist with."
OL,17,FHe added, "It's a great charity, but
OL,18,Funfortunately, like any charity, it
OL,19,Fcould do with a little more support
OL,20,Fand help."
